<Draft>
<Para><Text>Order made by the Scottish Ministers, laid before the Scottish Parliament under section 14(5)(b) of the Convention Rights (Compliance) (Scotland) Act 2001 for approval by resolution of the Scottish Parliament within 120 days beginning with 9th September 2015, being the date on which the Police Act 1997 and the Protection of Vulnerable Groups (Scotland) Act 2007 Remedial Order 2015 was made, not taking into account periods of dissolution or recess for more than 4 days.</Text></Para>
</Draft>
